content:
Add MobilePush to Your Flutter Mobile Apps

Integrate MobilePush functionality, including run-time toggles and custom mobile app events, with the new MobilePush Flutter plug-in. Send personalized mobile app messages that enhance user engagement and drive business results.

Where: This change applies to all Marketing Cloud Engagement editions.

When: The plugin is available for download on April 1, 2024.

How: Download and integrate the MobilePush Flutter plug-in using Pub.
title: Adding Custom Mobile Apps to Salesforce
